  bot.command("help", async (ctx) => {
    await ctx.reply(
      "Supported sources: TikTok and X.

Public content only: If the post is private, age-restricted, geo-blocked, deleted, or requires login, I can’t download it.

Common reasons it fails:
1) The link is not a direct TikTok video link or X status link
2) The content is restricted or removed
3) Telegram rejects the upload because the file is too large
4) Temporary network issues

Privacy: I don’t ask for logins. I only fetch the public URL you send and return the media into this chat."
    );
  });
}

